Admin | Full access to the system including user management, settings, and reports.

HR Manager | Manages employee records, recruitment, onboarding, and HR reports.

HR Staff | Assists with employee data entry, documentation, and HR processes.

Payroll Officer | Handles salary processing, deductions, and payroll reports.

Team Leader | Supervises team members, monitors performance, and assigns tasks.

Employee | Basic access to personal profile, attendance, and company updates.

IT Support | Responsible for system maintenance, troubleshooting, and technical support.

Finance Officer | Manages financial records, expenses, and budgeting reports.

Operations Manager | Oversees daily operations and ensures workflow efficiency.

Intern | Limited access role for trainees and temporary staff.